    <h1>My favourite animals</h1>
    <p>My favourite animals are dogs and cats. I like dogs because they are loyal and friendly. I like cats because they are independent and playful.</p>
    <p>Dogs are great companions and can be trained to do many things. They are also good for security and can protect their owners. Cats are great for keeping pests away and can be very affectionate. They are also great for people who live in apartments because they don't need as much space as dogs.</p> 
    <p>Overall, I think both dogs and cats are wonderful animals and I love them both!</p> 
     
